description: Life is no game on the world of the Gammarauders. But that won't stop you from playing along with the weirdest adventures ever concocted, courtesy of the team-up between DC Comics and TSR games. Based on the popular TSR combat game, GAMMARAUDERS tells the story of what happens when a bevy of bioborgs goes berserk on the world of Gammarauders, a crazy world of cryptic alliances between giant animal-warrior bioborgs and their human controllers. And if you think you know what to expect on this wild world of machine/monster madness...think again, because GAMMARAUDERS is no ordinary adventure.
name: Shut Down On The Big Nada

description: The Earth has seen better days...and its survivors just might find them again, if they can unite their warring factions under the banner of the Gammarauders against the attacking Slugnoids.
name: Shut Down Vol 2:Voice of the Turtle

description: The Slugnoids attack, but things aren't as desperate as they seem, because there's always Squawwk the Penguinoid to come to the rescue.
name: No Place to Raise a Giant Penguin

description: The bioborgs are the last hope for civilization as we know it...which isn't good news, considering that they're hopelessly outnumbered deep in the heart of Slugnoid territory.
name: Leader of the Pack!

description: The Rosebud Rumble - Part 1 of 4. Jok Tadsworth and fellow bioborg handlers have the Slugnoids hot on their heels...and a biomorphic horror that's part bioborg, part mutated podnoid, and all trouble in front of them.
name: The Rosebud Rumble - Part 1:Flat-Out Stoked on the Genome Freeway!

description: The Rosebud Rumble - Part 2 of 4. It's a totally rad time for all involved as Slash and Warlord Sassin slug it out for leadership of the Slugnoids...and those glitzy gals in prom dresses and Uzis, the Radical Debs, debut.
name: The Rosebud Rumble - Part 2: Do Not Forsake Me, O My Darling!

description: The Rosebud Rumble - Part 3 of 4. Can Jok regain control of the Sword That Was Broken in time to help save his fellow 'borg handlers?
name: The Rosebud Rumble 3: Ring Around the Collar!

description: The Rosebud Rumble - Part 4 of 4. Jok Tadsworth seeks the third talisman he needs to defeat Rosebud. There's only one snag, however: Rosebud has it.
name: The Kirward Derby - The Conclusion Of "The Rosebud Rumble"

description: Allisdau just wants Jok to notice her, so she gets him named to a seat in Congress. Afraid he'll notice them, the Cryptic Alliance tries to remove him from office...by killing him.
name: We'd Like To Help You, Son, But You're Too Weird To Vote!

description: Final issue. It's showdown time on the Big Nada as Jok becomes the target for every disgruntled member of the Slugnoids and the Cryptic Alliances.
name: Every Bioborg My Enemy!

description: re-prints All star Western #7,11 and Weird Western Tales #13, 23-24, and 39.
